highlights: Installed and repaired various radio equipment, including multichannel radio systems, to support ground and aviation forces, ensuring reliable communication networks.

Conducted troubleshooting on combinations of radio sets, terminals, and associated devices to maintain uninterrupted service for end users, identifying and rectifying faults with precision and expertise.
Mentored, supervised, and led the professional and personal development of 10 junior personnel during this role.
